### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health

### Signup by username
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Login by username
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

